nhc_headline: ...KELI MOVING QUICKLY WESTWARD WHILE MAINTAINING ITS INTENSITY...
summary: ...KELI MOVING QUICKLY WESTWARD WHILE MAINTAINING ITS INTENSITY... As of 5:00 PM HST Tue Jul 29 the center of Keli was located near 13.1, -151.7 with movement W at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
